Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔的頂端?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才埃洱又看了那本古書才注意到這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一段是這麼寫的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『在這通天劍塔之上有個惡魔棲息在頂端』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個惡魔棲息在...頂端...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個所謂的惡魔就是魔石索沙的主人的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼....現在就應該站在這個劍塔的最頂端才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙的...主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本古書上面所寫的未必全都是真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是應該上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們手邊也沒有什麼其他的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢?克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先躲到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能肯定......
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來一定比以前還要危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把妳帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳把蕾娜帶到雷恩他們身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要留在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什麼勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有信心能夠保證妳平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會成為你們的絆腳石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就答應我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼決定嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就跟著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧?蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓，你們有沒有怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你還受到魔物的詛咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是吉耐的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠是魔族地位最崇高的...吉耐王...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根羽毛已經加持了守護的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它插在那把劍上...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護的力量...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然...為了拿到這根羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顧自己生命危險去找吉耐?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事還等著你去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會再見到面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭...蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳吼破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會讓你們對艾斯貝爾為所欲為的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼......
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會....有這種感覺呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直忐忑不安......
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德，你和蕾娜先走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有我和艾修頓來擋住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴......
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得讓我有個大顯身子的機會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼啦?大哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古書上的解讀是怎麼說的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個章節是這麼寫的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『一切的命運最後都將交託於神聖之光』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『只要能夠有人出現將這道聖潔的光輝導向正軌』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『就還是有可能將惡魔毀於無形...』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們完蛋了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥啊...我有點不太懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唸的....到底是什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面所謂的光輝，當然就是拉克爾赫普了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們既然把機會漏失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有什麼希望可言呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說我們這個星球，注定是要滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們懂了沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球啊......
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要滅亡......
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大...那怎麼辦啊?我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭什麼!我也很痛苦.....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個在胡說八道什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克爾赫普沒有把\N魔石索沙擊毀，那就表示這個星球要毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂講!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到這把年紀還沒什麼成就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做什麼都得要有自信才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有工作又身無分文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到今天還沒結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是活該
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳也不用這樣說我們嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個為什麼就不能學著什麼事都向前看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣會有用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克爾赫普，這一次的確是沒有把敵人給打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們只要還有一條命在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就有機會可以改變現況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照時間看來...\N克勞德他們現在一定已經入侵到魔石索沙裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德這一次可是豁出性命來打這場仗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了保護我們這個星球，可是想盡了各種方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果放棄就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那本古書上的預言是怎麼寫的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這場戰爭還沒有結束...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示我們還有一絲希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在應該做什麼好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼....我們可以幫的上忙的地方嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我打算把那艘太空船修好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們幾個幫得了忙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以囉，我還是個機械白癡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只要照我說的做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於太難的部分，自然會由我們來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話真不錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我過去從沒有相信過什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得身體...好熱...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這種感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到路呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有條路會通到上面去才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路啊...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，她不是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點，來吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,階梯...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳吼破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量光箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有魄力怎麼行呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們都把我的皮膚弄成這個樣子了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看只是瘀青....沒什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，有種就給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的工作就是盡可能把這些怪物攔在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小長，小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在誰想要單挑就來找我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖殿?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙裡......怎麼會有這種地方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是......
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜......
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜.....終於見到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等著見妳的這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過沒想到我們會在這樣的情況下見面...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳是同一種人尼德行星的子民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼德行星?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳胸前的那個墜子就是尼德子民的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪妳會這麼驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟在這之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直以為妳是這個艾斯貝爾星上的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳確實跟我們屬於同一個族類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙就掌控在我們的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙掌控在你們的手中?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止對決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如跟我們一起在這裡保護魔石索沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要......
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說的不是真的，對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是他們的族人......
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們掌控的魔石索沙...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要毀滅這個艾斯貝爾星...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就是在這裡出生長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜......
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再跟在你身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒有資格再跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一心想保住這個星球的平安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼啊?蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也變成你的敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠保住這個星球獻出了性命，奮力一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定......
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把妳當作自己人看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德......
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的左手完全沒有力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在搞什麼東西啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算修好了有什麼用啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎部分是雷恩負責的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼修的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還怪我，根本是妳操作不當!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪也該怪普莉西絲才對!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都什麼時候了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要吵架啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使不出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德......
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在......
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫他...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的...想助他一臂之力...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保護我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡誕生才能遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我是那些敵人的族人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的心...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠向著艾斯貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人和朋友都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪裡出生的根本不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的故鄉...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡.......就是你們這趟旅程的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問.......妳到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是終點?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到我的城堡......

